" /><br />\n如果中學冇讀過商科去到大學讀商科catch 唔catch up 到<br />\n同埋想問下由faculty of science 轉去 faculty of business or art 難唔難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩晒各位<br />\n<br />\n最後大家香港人一定要加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"我中學都冇讀econ同bafs。今個sem讀緊econ1210, 其實都算ok, 只不過佢教得真係好快，要自己返去睇返。<br />\n<br />\n至於你話transfer 過嚟E&amp;F或者BBA，我估gpa應該要3左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T19:36:55.000Z","msg":"FBE infamous 爛grade course Econ 1210<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3721f5e6bec9959e096745cd95468377b024a7d","tid":1655374,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45117a20043a0596a92e14f7f114faf814573174","tid":1655374,"uid":325928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c4b6e09103a3597f6a5e88ae185ab8f8e07a1a5","tid":1655374,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d93ac60f2bfba2eb4f230b110973de5311dc23da","tid":1655374,"uid":325928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:31:34.000Z","msg":"而家個CC都幾好<br />\n其實free elective 姐係點<br />\n我覺得我自己好似個白痴好多野都唔清楚<br />\n介唔介意解釋多少少<br />\n麻煩曬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:35:17.000Z","msg":"即係 唔係minor 唔係major 唔係cc 唔係core language<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:59:25.000Z","msg":"即係自己揀嘅冇相關嘅course 黎讀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20